```


:::
:::



### Rows



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
row_sums <- apply(
  X = df,               # dataframe input
  MARGIN = 1,           # apply over rows
  FUN = sum             # function: `sum()`
)

row_sums
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
